"{\"uid\": \"propakistani.pk-2024-07-29-blasphemous-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-hurts-religious-sentiments\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The opening ceremony of theParis Summer Olympicson Friday night ignited a global controversy after featuring a parody of Leonardo Da Vinci's iconic painting \\\"The Last Supper,\\\" depicted by drag queens.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 200, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 121, \"end\": 129, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1660089615949e-15, \"text\": \"Leonardo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}, {\"begin\": 130, \"end\": 138, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.327340107344615e-28, \"text\": \"Da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The scene has been criticized by many as \\\"shocking and insulting to Christian people around the world.\\\"\", \"from\": 201, \"to\": 304, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 269, \"end\": 278, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9994267145332336, \"rank\": 0.0005736142994467961, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the ceremony, broadcast cameras revealed a long table overlooking the Seine River, where drag performers emulated Jesus Christ and the 12 apostles in a scene reminiscent of Da Vinci's famous fresco.\", \"from\": 306, \"to\": 511, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 427, \"end\": 439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999929747906504, \"rank\": 7.02525868944523e-06, \"text\": \"Jesus Christ\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}, {\"begin\": 486, \"end\": 494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.327340107344615e-28, \"text\": \"Da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This depiction immediately drew widespread criticism, with many questioning its appropriateness in such a global event.\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 631, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Among the vocal critics was former talk show host Piers Morgan, who questioned the decision, asking, \\\"Would they have mocked any other religion like this?\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 787, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 683, \"end\": 695, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Piers_Morgan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Piers Morgan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Piers_Morgan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Piers_Morgan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Appalling decision.\\\"\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 808, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Donald Trump Jr. echoed these sentiments, sharing a photo of the scene with the caption, \\\"They are not even pretending anymore,\\\" while Elon Musk, the CEO of SpaceX, Tesla, and X (formerly Twitter), called the parody \\\"extremely disrespectful to Christians.\\\"\", \"from\": 809, \"to\": 1065, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 809, \"end\": 825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump_Jr.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Donald Trump Jr.\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump_Jr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump_Jr.\"}, {\"begin\": 944, \"end\": 953, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Elon Musk\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\"}, {\"begin\": 974, \"end\": 979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nikola_Tesla\", \"score\": 0.6708732637187599, \"rank\": 0.49059450432825225, \"text\": \"Tesla\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nikola_Tesla\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nikola_Tesla\"}, {\"begin\": 997, \"end\": 1004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.722573924003427e-23, \"text\": \"Twitter\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\"}, {\"begin\": 1053, \"end\": 1063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.973439933804441, \"rank\": 0.018978172439162576, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Religious leaders also expressed their disapproval.\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1118, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Minnesota Bishop Robert Barron, a well-known Catholic figure in the U.S., described it as a \\\"gross mockery\\\" and a reflection of a \\\"deeply secularist postmodern society.\\\"\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1288, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1119, \"end\": 1128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota\", \"score\": 0.9999997039754346, \"rank\": 1.6697633962864764e-07, \"text\": \"Minnesota\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota\"}, {\"begin\": 1136, \"end\": 1149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Barron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.8795582780716155e-26, \"text\": \"Robert Barron\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Barron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Barron\"}, {\"begin\": 1164, \"end\": 1172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9999975645016648, \"rank\": 2.1049954218987074e-06, \"text\": \"Catholic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Similarly, Wisconsin-based Bishop Donald Hying labeled the act as \\\"blasphemy,\\\" and Texas-based Bishop Daniel Flores lamented that both athletes and people of Christian faith deserve more respect than what was portrayed.\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1316, \"end\": 1322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bishop\", \"score\": 0.9999189470971543, \"rank\": 8.105735529478108e-05, \"text\": \"Bishop\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bishop\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bishop\"}, {\"begin\": 1384, \"end\": 1390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bishop\", \"score\": 0.9999189470971543, \"rank\": 8.105735529478108e-05, \"text\": \"Bishop\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bishop\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bishop\"}, {\"begin\": 1391, \"end\": 1404, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Flores\", \"score\": 0.9998668879328672, \"rank\": 0.00013312978655939867, \"text\": \"Daniel Flores\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Flores\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Flores\"}, {\"begin\": 1447, \"end\": 1456, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9994267145332336, \"rank\": 0.0005736142994467961, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The backlash extended beyond the United States, with some interpreting the scene as a message to Christians that they are \\\"NOT WELCOME.\\\"\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1646, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1543, \"end\": 1556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9998383116402554, \"rank\": 0.00013750232498564022, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1607, \"end\": 1617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.973439933804441, \"rank\": 0.018978172439162576, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Others criticized the inclusion of a white horse carrying the Olympic flag, interpreting it as a reference to the pale horse of the Book of Revelation, often associated with death.\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1827, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In response to the outcry, the International Olympic Committee (IOC) issued a formal apology on Sunday.\", \"from\": 1829, \"to\": 1932, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1860, \"end\": 1897, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A statement from the IOC emphasized that the intention was not to disrespect any religious group but to promote tolerance and community.\", \"from\": 1933, \"to\": 2069, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1954, \"end\": 1957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.392692853515384e-18, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Clearly there was never any intention to show disrespect to any religious group.\", \"from\": 2071, \"to\": 2152, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On the contrary, we intended to show tolerance and community.\", \"from\": 2153, \"to\": 2214, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If people have taken any offense then we are sorry,\\\" said Paris 2024 spokesperson Anne Descamps at a press conference.\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2333, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2273, \"end\": 2283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.484728588731234e-18, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2302, \"end\": 2310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\ud83d\\udce2 For the latest Sports news, videos and analysis join ProPakistani's WhatsApp Group now!\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2424, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow ProPakistani on Google News & scroll through your favourite content faster!\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2508, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Shares  Free Speech kaha gai ab  ProPakistani is the premier and most trustworthy resource \\tfor all happenings in technology, telecom, business, sports, auto, education, real estate and entertainment news in Pakistan.Whether it's the top trending news, ins